# Browser Rendering Engine
#
# Sits between the UI library and the 2D engine in the rendering stack:
#   Apps -> UI Lib -> Browser Engine (this) -> 2D Engine -> Backend
#
# Takes a DOM/CSS tree (from UI widgets or HTML) and renders it using
# the 2D engine's drawing primitives.

